its-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/">Idol社 収益の75%を所属VTuberに還元 異例の公開に踏み切った背景は</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;Idol社 収益の75%を所属VTuberに還元 異例の公開に踏み切った背景は&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/idol-corporation-returns-75-percent-of-profits-to-vtuber-what-is-the-background-behind-the-unusual-disclosure/embed/#?secret=PNkmY4ry06#?secret=ziEXSx7zOZ" data-secret="ziEXSx7zOZ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Dp1ghQHVVV"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/gossip-vtuber-claims-nijisanji-talents-earns-only-2-3-profit-from-merch-sales/">ゴシップ系VTuber「にじさんじ所属タレントがグッズ販売で得る利益は2~3%」と一方的に主張</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;ゴシップ系VTuber「にじさんじ所属タレントがグッズ販売で得る利益は2~3%」と一方的に主張&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/gossip-vtuber-claims-nijisanji-talents-earns-only-2-3-profit-from-merch-sales/embed/#?secret=EvJHD91d2n#?secret=Dp1ghQHVVV" data-secret="Dp1ghQHVVV" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://youtube.com/@AzuraCecillia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Azura Cecillia Ch.">Azura Cecillia Ch.</a> ／ <a href="https://twitter.com/Azura_Cecillia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Azura Cecillia">Azura Cecillia</a></p> <cite>YouTube / X (Twitter)</cite></blockquote><p> ( <em>P2y.jp 管理代表者「2号さん (仮)」</em> ／バーチャル・メタバース・VTuber情報) </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret